Individual — Available Functionality                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
  Profile & Identity                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  - View/update personal info, address, business info, security settings                                                                                                                                                            - Contact verification (email/phone) with OTP                                                                                                                                                                                     - Master PIN setup, change, and ban removal                                                                                                                                                                                     

  KYC / Documents

  - Upload, view, update, delete media files (KYC documents)
  - Submit profile documents for compliance review
  - View KYC providers and verification items
  - Reset identification

  Transaction Confirmation Settings

  - Configure OTP/PIN confirmation per transaction type
  - View and update confirmation settings

  Wallet / Accounts

  - View, create, rename, close, delete accounts
  - Set main account, validate account numbers
  - Get deposit address (cryptocurrency)
  - View account closing requests

  In-System Cards

  - Create, view, delete own in-system cards linked to accounts

  Bank Accounts

  - Add, view, delete bank accounts linked to in-system accounts

  Transfers

  - Perform in-system transfers + fee calculation
  - Create, use, and delete transfer templates

  Top-Up

  - Top-up via bank transfer (create request, accept, decline)
  - Top-up via cash desk

  Withdrawal

  - Withdraw via bank (create request, accept, execute)
  - Withdraw via cash desk
  - Create, use, and delete withdrawal templates

  Invoices

  - Create, view, and pay invoices
  - Calculate invoice fees (as payer)

  External / Provider Operations

  - Provider-based top-up, withdrawal, and purchase (create, calculate, accept)
  - Issue payment cards via provider + fee calculation

  Transactions & Reporting

  - View, categorize, add notes to transactions
  - Confirm transactions with OTP/PIN
  - View grouped external-process transactions
  - Account balance overview, outflow/income summaries by category

  OTP / Confirmations

  - View pending confirmations, resend OTP, confirm operations

  Company Management (KYC-approved Individuals only)

  - Create companies, add representatives and shareholders
  - Submit company for compliance review, open company accounts

