  Merchant — Available Functionality

  Everything Individual Has, Plus:

  Merchant Payments

  - Create, view, cancel merchant payments
  - View payment details

  Points of Sale (POS)

  - Create, view, update, delete POS terminals
  - View transactions per POS

  Product Catalog

  - Create, update, delete products (including batch operations)
  - Update/delete products by external code

  Product Categories

  - Create, update, delete product categories

  Product Measure Units

  - Create, update, delete measure units (including batch and by external code)

  Product Pricing

  - Create, update, delete product prices

  Invoice Templates

  - Create, view, delete invoice templates for reuse

  Invoices (Enhanced)

  - Calculate merchant-side commission for invoice creation (separate from payer-side)

  ---
  Shared (Both Roles)

  Profile, KYC, bank accounts, wallets, in-system cards, transfers, top-ups, withdrawals, invoices (create/pay), external provider operations, transaction history, reporting, OTP confirmations.

  Exclusive to Merchant

  POS management, merchant payments, product catalog (products, categories, measure units, pricing), invoice templates, merchant commission calculation.

  Exclusive to Individual

  Company onboarding (creating companies with representatives, shareholders — for KYC-approved Individuals only).